== About GUCoach ==
This application manages your Goalunited team player data.
Player data is imported from CSV files and persisted to an embedded database.

Warning: The software is in alpha stage! Use at your own risk.

== Planned functionality ==
- show all player information in a table view
- provide lots of different statistics showing the development of each player and the entire team
- calculate the best line-up for the next match
- forecast future development of the team based on collected data

== Help wanted ==
I'm looking for Java enthusiasts - especially JavaFX 2.0 programmers - who would like to help developing GUCoach.
Please feel free to checkout sources at https://github.com/mwalter/GUCoach.
Your ideas and improvements are welcome!